# OPENSORCERY API
API for http://opensorcery.me

## Project [/projects/{id}]
Represents a single project.

Required attributes: 

- `id`              The unique ID of the Project
- `name`            The name of the Project
- `github_url`      The url of the Project on GitHub
- `languages`       A list of languages used in the Project
- `contributors`    A list of contributors of the Project
- `description`     A description of the Projecthttp://docs.opensorcery.apiary.io/traffic

+ Parameters
    + name (required, string) ... Unique name

+ Model (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                "name": "Example Project",
                "github_url" : "http://github.com/example_projct"
                "languages" : ["JavaScript", "Python"],
                "contributors": ["user1", "user2"],
                "owner": "Google"
            }
            
## Retrieve a single Project [GET]

+ Response 200

    [Project][]
    
+ Response 404 (application/json)

        "Resource not found" 


