## List all projects [GET]

+ Response 200

    [Project List][]

## Company [/companies/{name}]
Represents a single company.

Required attributes: 

- `name`            The name of the company
- `projects`        A list of projects owned by the Company
- `members`         A list of contributors that belong to this company
- `description`     A description of the company

+ Parameters
    + name (required, string) ... Unique name

+ Model (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                "name": "Google",
                "github_url" : "http://github.com/google",
                "projects": ["project1", "project2"],
                "members": ["user1", "user2"],
                "description": "Google is a a company focused on ..."
            }
            
## Retrieve a single Company [GET]

+ Response 200

    [Company][]
    
+ Response 404 (application/json)

        "Resource not found" 


# Company List [/companies]
Get all companies.

