## List all companies [GET]

+ Response 200

    [Company List][]

## Contributor [/contributors/{username}]
Represents a single contributor.

Required attributes: 

- `username`  The username of the contributor
- `email`     The email address of the contributor
- `projects`  A list of projects this contributor contributed to

+ Parameters
    + username (required, string) ... Unique username

+ Model (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                "username": "example_name",
                "email": "example@example.com",
                "github_url": http://github.com/user1,
                "projects": ["project1", "project2"],
                "companies": ["Google", "Microsoft"]
            }
            
## Retrieve a single Contributor [GET]

+ Response 200

    [Contributor][]
    
+ Response 404 (application/json)

        "Resource not found" 


